    "Since the gold labels for the test set were disclosed, Figure 2 presents the confusion matrix that categorizes product reviews into Human and AI predicted.",
    "The figure indicates that out of 200 reviews, 180 were accurately predicted.",
    "Al reviews (13) predicted more incorrectly compare to Human reviews (7), this occurred because AI can generate humanoid reviews.",
    "And for short-length data (less than or equal to 10 words), our proposed model perform better than large length of data.",
    "The proposed models only trained on the given dataset."
  ]
